  "detailed_description": "Larry's Christmas tree has been telling him to kill. But whose side is the tree really on? And can he trust what he's hearing?<br><br>CHRISTMAS MASSACRE is an 80's inspired stealth slasher game with low-poly, PS1-style graphics. Sneak, stalk and murder your prey without being caught. You must kill without being seen to complete each level.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1840490/extras/73dd1880f240ac97ade491ab53c3c004.poster.avif?t=1671911494\" width=428 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1840490/extras/73dd1880f240ac97ade491ab53c3c004.webm?t=1671911494\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1840490/extras/73dd1880f240ac97ade491ab53c3c004.mp4?t=1671911494\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Multiple masks and costumes<br></li><li> Arcade style stealth<br></li><li> Fast Forward Button<br></li><li> Drenched with gore<br></li><li> First and third person camera models<br></li><li> Crusty PS1-style graphics</li></ul>",
